item.title: Google's New Golang SDK for Protobuf
item.description: Google has released a new Golang SDK for protobuf. In the [announcement], a useful tool to redact properties is described. If like me, this is somewhat novel to you, here’s a mashup using Google’s Protocol Buffer Basics w/ redaction. To be very clear, as it’s an important distinction: Version Repo Docs v2 google.golang.org/protobuf Docs v1 github.com/golang/protobuf Docs Project Here’s my project structure:
